This is a factory new in box Springfield XDs 9 with 4" barrel. It has a slim grip and slide at .90" making this handgun extremely easy to conceal. It comes with  2 magazines, one holds a standard 7 rounds and the other is slightly longer holding 8 rounds. It also comes with magazine holder, paddle holster, lock, and manual. There are also an extra magazine sleeve and base plate to accommodate which magazine you'd prefer and carry method.

This pistol is perfect for conceal carry with a standard sized barrel and a short grip. Providing a longer sight radius and still small where it counts. This means your clothes dont have to be as baggy as you think!

for sale by Citizen Soldier Armory (www.csarmory.com)
